       ≡ Sensitive<gaze|biometric|face|body> structurally-banned-from feature-set

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ ROLE-DM  «orchestrator · scene-arbiter · intent-router-master»

  § RESPONSIBILITIES
    scene-arbitration         : ambiguity-resolver-between competing-Intent
    intent-routing-master     : final-target-selection over per-target-cap-table
    scene-graph-build         : story-DAG construction-via causal-seed
    pacing-controller-handoff : tension-target-vec → GM @ S3-dispatch boundary

  § SUPPORT-CRATES
    cssl-host-causal-seed     : story-as-physics DAG ; branch-merge primitives
    cssl-host-attestation     : audit aggregation per-role-scope
    cssl-host-rt-trace        : per-decision instrumentation ; replay-anchor
    cssl-intent-router        : dispatch-target selection (W3b landed)
    cssl-host-cocreative      : bias-vector consume @ stage-0

  § INPUTS
    intent_router::Intent     : typed-Intent { variant, confidence, payload }
    ω-field-state-summary     : current-zone + radiance + spawn-zone-occupancy
    player-history-buffer     : last-N=8 Intent + last-M=4 manifestations
    cocreative-bias-vector    : 16-D f32'norm preference-tensor (cssl-host-cocreative)

  § OUTPUTS
    scene-edit-op             : (kind, location, attribs) → Stage-S4 seed-stamp
    spawn-order               : Intent::SpawnCondensation re-emission @ DM-bias
    npc-spawn-request         : NPC-handle + zone + cap-pre-grant
    companion-prompt          : text-hash → vercel companion-proxy (cap-gated)

  § CAP-GATING  ‼
    DM_CAP_SCENE_EDIT      = 1   : stamp seed-cells via SubstrateMutateCap-zone
    DM_CAP_SPAWN_NPC       = 2   : NPC instantiation via Sovereign-claim-grant
    DM_CAP_COMPANION_RELAY = 4   : forward-text-hash via NetPostWriteCap
    sovereign-bypass-recorded   : sovereign-act-as logs sovereign.bypass-event ‼

  § STAGE-0  «heuristic decision-tree»  ⟪ shipped @ b69165c ⟫
    rule-table : (intent-variant × scene-state × history) → action-tag
    determinism : table-lookup ; replay-bit-equal given snapshot
    no-LLM-roundtrip ; no-online-learning
    ≡ "DM-as-physical-process" not "DM-as-thinking-being"

  § STAGE-1  «KAN-substrate ride»  ⟪ deferred W6 ⟫
    cssl-substrate-kan spline-table replaces-rule-branches ; bias-vec via-spline
    invariant : Σ-mask-aware · replay-deterministic · bakeable @ comptime
    fallback  : stage-0 retained-as graceful-degradation-path

  § FAILURE-MODES
    cap-revoked-mid       : DROP+user-feedback ; defer-to-GM-narration ‼
    intent-confidence-low : DROP-to-Unknown ; route-DM-fallback @ S3
    no-action-fallback    : SILENT-PASS counter-incr ; ¬ spawn ; await-next-Intent
    sovereign-mismatch    : SIG0003 compile-time ‼ ; ¬ runtime-attempt

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ ROLE-GM  «narrator · text-emitter · pacing-controller»

  § RESPONSIBILITIES
    narrative-text-emission   : prose-snippet from scene-state + Φ-tags
    pacing-control            : prose-rhythm matched-to DM-tension-target
    player-prompt-generation  : "what would you like to do?" UI-prompts
    text-tone-adjustment      : tone-lever from cocreative-bias (warm | terse | poetic)

  § SUPPORT-CRATES
    cssl-host-voice           : TTS abstraction ⟪ planned W6 ⟫ ◐ stub-W5
    cssl-host-cocreative      : player-pref bias-vector consumption
    cssl-host-attestation     : per-emission audit
    cssl-rt                   : text-frame stream into UI (cssl-runtime/text_input.cssl)

  § INPUTS
    DM-scene-state            : zone + companion-presence + radiance + tension-target
    player-text-or-voice      : Intent::DialogGM payload
    style-preferences         : cocreative-bias { warm: f32, terse: f32, poetic: f32 }
    Φ-handle-tags @ cells     : 10000-D HDC semantic-tags from-substrate

  § OUTPUTS
    narrative-text-frame      : English-prose UTF-8 ; user-facing-OK
    prompt-suggestion         : list<string> ; player-selectable hint-pool
    pacing-mark-event         : { kind: rise|hold|fall, magnitude, ts }

  § CAP-GATING  ‼
    GM_CAP_TEXT_EMIT       = 1   : write to UI-text-buffer (in-process)
    GM_CAP_VOICE_EMIT      = 2   : TTS audio-frame emission (W6) ⟪ deferred ⟫
    GM_CAP_TONE_TUNE       = 4   : apply tone-lever from cocreative-bias

  § STAGE-0  «templated phrases + cocreative-bias selection»
    template-table : (zone × event-class × tone) → prose-template-id
    fill-in : Φ-tag-driven slot-filling (e.g. "you see {Φ-handle-tag}")
    determinism : seed = (template-id × Φ-tags-hash × bias-vec-hash)
    English-OK : per Apocky-CLAUDE.md user-facing-allowed-context

  § STAGE-1  «KAN-narrative-LM-ride»  ⟪ deferred W6 ⟫
    cssl-substrate-kan trained-narrative-LM · tone-conditioned · on-device-only
    fallback : stage-0 templates always-available

  § FAILURE-MODES
    silent-text        : GM_CAP_TEXT_EMIT-revoked → SILENT-PASS+counter ; ¬ panic
    degrade-to-generic : Φ-tag-miss → "you see something here" generic-prompt
    tts-fail           : DEGRADE-text-only ; user-warning ; ¬ pipeline-halt

