§ ROLE-COLLABORATOR  «co-author · player-suggestion-integrator»

  § RESPONSIBILITIES
    player-suggestion-integration : "I want X" → scene-edit-op draft
    story-branch-merge            : co-edited-branch ⊕ canonical-branch resolution
    co-creative-loop-driver       : iterative-refinement gradient (player-feedback)

  § SUPPORT-CRATES
    cssl-host-cocreative          : the-gradient-optimizer (W4 landed)
    cssl-host-causal-seed         : branch-merge DAG primitives
    cssl-host-attestation         : per-suggestion audit
    cssl-mcp-server               : MCP-tool surface for save-scene/load-scene

  § INPUTS
    player-edit-suggestions       : open-vocabulary text → typed-suggestion
    player-thumbs-up-down         : f32 ∈ [-1, +1] feedback signal
    player-typed-alternatives     : list<text-hash> branch-candidates
    cap-state                     : SubstrateMutateCap available?

  § OUTPUTS
    merged-story-state            : DAG-node-set after-merge
    revised-cocreative-bias-vec   : 16-D f32'norm updated-preference-tensor
    branch-state-diff             : { added, removed, conflicted } cell-coord-sets

  § CAP-GATING  ‼
    COLLAB_CAP_INTEGRATE      = 1   : draft scene-edit-op (no-apply-yet)
    COLLAB_CAP_BRANCH_MERGE   = 2   : commit branch-merge to causal-seed DAG
    COLLAB_CAP_BIAS_UPDATE    = 4   : write cocreative-bias-vec to-store

  § STAGE-0  «cocreative gradient + heuristic merge»
    gradient : Adam-like step over bias-vec ; lr=0.01 ; β1=0.9 ; β2=0.999
    merge-policy : last-write-wins ⊕ Σ-mask-conflict-defer
    determinism : seeded-RNG per-merge ; replay-bit-equal
    bias-vec stored-LOCAL : per-installation salted ; opt-in-egress @ Sovereign-grant

  § STAGE-1  «KAN-merge-policy»  ⟪ deferred W6 ⟫
    cssl-substrate-kan trained-merge-policy · conflict-resolution learned-from-history
    fallback : stage-0 heuristic always-available

  § FAILURE-MODES
    reject-with-reason       : Σ-mask-conflict → user-msg + DROP ; ¬ silent-fail
